\sum_{i=0}^{n}\binom{2n+1}{i}=2^{2n}
[1,2,3,..,2n]
\displaystyle \sum_{i=0}^{n}\binom{2n+1}{i}=2^{2n}
2^{2n+1}=\sum_{i=0}^{2n+1}\binom{2n+1}{i}=\sum_{i=0}^{n}\binom{2n+1}{i}+\sum_{i=n+1}^{2n+1}\binom{2n+1}{i}=
\sum_{i=0}^{n}\binom{2n+1}{i}+\sum_{i=n+1}^{2n+1}\binom{2n+1}{2n+1-i}=
\sum_{i=0}^{n}\binom{2n+1}{i}+\sum_{j=0}^{n}\binom{2n+1}{j}=2\sum_{i=0}^{n}\binom{2n+1}{i}.
